item.title: CVE-2022-29511|2024-09-16T17:24:12.936Z -- lansweeper -- lansweeper
item.description: A directory traversal vulnerability exists in the KnowledgebasePageActions.aspx ImportArticles functionality of Lansweeper lansweeper 10.1.1.0. A specially-crafted HTTP request can lead to arbitrary file read. An attacker can send an HTTP request to trigger this vulnerability.
